From: Nickel Browser Team <team@nickel-browser.org>
Date: Thu, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Nickel Browser: Remove Google API Keys

This patch ensures no Google API keys are used in the build,
preventing any communication with Google services that require authentication.

---
 google_apis/google_api_keys.cc | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/google_apis/google_api_keys.cc b/google_apis/google_api_keys.cc
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/google_apis/google_api_keys.cc
+++ b/google_apis/google_api_keys.cc
@@ -20,6 +20,10 @@

 namespace google_apis {

+bool HasKeysWithValidFormat() {
+  return false;
+}
+
 std::string GetAPIKey() {
   return "";
 }
--
2.40.0
